      "body": "```suggestion\r\nOctojoin achieves partial obfuscation similar to Monero's ring signatures ([https://www.getmonero.org/2024/04/27/fcmps.html FCMP++] will replace ring signatures in the future) and stealth addresses. Swaps can be done off-chain to obscure the transaction's input ownership and history.\r\n```",
